### Create a Passage for a Story
POST http://localhost:8080/api/stories/1/passages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Opening Scene",
  "content": "It was a dark and stormy night...",
  "order": 1,
  "author": "Alice"
}

### Get All Passages for a Story
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stories/1/passages
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Passage by ID for a Story
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stories/1/passages/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Update Passage for a Story
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/stories/1/passages/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Opening Scene (Edited)",
  "content": "The storm raged on...",
  "order": 1,
  "author": "Alice"
}

### Delete Passage for a Story
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/stories/1/passages/1
Content-Type: application/json
